{"tid":1637300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普︰香港示威或不利於中美經貿談判","createTime":"2019-10-08T02:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T03:33:31.000Z","uid":1121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef038244f652f5f8eee9135c26efbe0fa9ccaf01","tid":1637300,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中美周四展開新一輪高級別經貿談判，美國總統特朗普指，香港的示威可能會不利於談判。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普︰「我們希望可以看到能以非常人道方式解決，我希望這事會發生。你知香港對全球非常重要，不僅是對中國來說，對世界亦然。我只希望可以看到達致一個人道協議，我知道習主席有能力做得到，我認為他是一個令人信服的人，我們正在談判。如果發生任何不好的事，我想會對談判不利，政治上可能會很困難，可能對於我們、其他某些人以及他（習近平），但我認為他們要以和平的態度處理。」"},{"pid":"c30eca47178b502c13a05205f5894b8770c76b81","tid":1637300,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"特朗普︰香港示威或不利於中美經貿談判<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365460&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365460%26refer%3DShare&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=ce637295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365460%26refer%3DShare&h=5c41ce97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365460&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"d8a02fd22e6005130f507d9116240a5ccfb3f845","tid":1637300,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W32rY0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW32rY0N.jpg&h=a4b0aa42&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}